description:
This week on ANN, the General Conference welcomes leaders worldwide for their Annual Council meetings.

For the first time in three years due to the COVID-19 pandemic, the 2022 Nationwide Pathfinder Bible Experience (PEB) was held on-site, on September 25, 2022, at Hankook Sahmyook High School in Seoul, South Korea.

ADRA mobilizes to provide aid to South Sudan, a country experiencing extreme flooding

Hope Channel shares the Adventist Church's challenges, achievements, and vision in India. These stories and more are coming up!

For more updates on worldwide Adventist news, subscribe to our Youtube channel. 

ANN is the official news channel of the Seventh-day Adventist Church. Visit https://adventist.news/ for the most recent Adventist news.
